<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/189296.Machete_Season"><img alt="Machete Season: The Killers in Rwanda Speak" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1431459739l/189296._SX98_.jpg" />
