<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/66419.When_Victims_Become_Killers"><img alt="When Victims Become Killers: Colonialism, Nativism, and the Genocide in Rwanda" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388515349l/66419._SX98_.jpg" />
